00:00:19,620 --> 00:00:22,980
我  艾薩克·沃爾頓
I, Isaac Walton...

18
00:00:25,040 --> 00:00:28,860
犯有窺探艾比蓋爾·庫克胴體
Have gazed upon the nakedness of Abigail Cook...

