還有手淫之罪
And committed the sin of self-pollution.

23
00:00:44,210 --> 00:00:45,570
用力給他十鞭
10 hard ones.

24
00:00:55,290 --> 00:00:56,940
就在今天
On this glorious day,

25
00:00:56,940 --> 00:00:59,300
我們的勇士集結于此
Our brave boys muster

26
00:00:59,300 --> 00:01:02,000
共同對抗惡魔的先遣部隊
to face the devil's shock troops...

27
00:01:02,290 --> 00:01:05,110
那些聚集在我們家門口的
French and Indian savages

28
00:01:05,120 --> 00:01:08,740
兇殘法國人及印第安野蠻人
massing in the woods right outside our doors.

29
00:01:09,450 --> 00:01:11,240
而你們要保衛的是什么呢
And what are you going off to defend?

30
00:01:11,610 --> 00:01:14,200
不是所多瑪  而是塞勒姆
Not Sodom, but Salem.

31
00:01:11,610 --> 00:01:14,200
{\an8}所多瑪是因其罪惡被上帝所滅的城鎮

32
00:01:14,820 --> 00:01:17,800
如果我們能容忍這種傷風敗俗的人或事
We cannot expect god to be on our side

33
00:01:17,810 --> 00:01:22,050
上帝還怎么保佑我們
if we tolerate abominations or those who commit them.

34
00:01:23,180 --> 00:01:25,770
你們倆將被通宵被鎖在這里
You two will remain in the stocks overnight.

35
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:28,850
而你小子  將一生背負
And you, boy, will bear the mark of your sins

36
00:01:28,860 --> 00:01:30,490
你罪孽的印記
the rest of your life.

37
00:01:35,020 --> 00:01:37,130
不要啊  求你了
No, please. Please!

38
00:01:37,130 --> 00:01:38,850
行行好吧  西布里
For god's sakes, Sibley.

39
00:01:39,520 --> 00:01:42,780
當眾羞辱和鞭刑已經夠他受的了
The stocks and the lashings are punishment enough.

40
00:01:43,440 --> 00:01:44,510
不要啊
No!

41
00:01:45,190 --> 00:01:46,600
私通者
Fornicator!

42
00:01:51,550 --> 00:01:52,670
"你們不要論斷人
Judge not...

43
00:01:54,230 --> 00:01:56,010
免得你們被論斷"
lest ye be judged.

44
00:01:54,230 --> 00:01:56,010
{\an8}出自圣經《馬太福音》第七章7:1

45
00:01:56,520 --> 00:01:57,630
誰在說話
Who said that?

46
00:01:58,370 --> 00:02:01,230
這是耶穌說的  你也許聽說過他
Jesus. You might have heard of him.

47
00:02:02,390 --> 00:02:03,570
約翰·奧登
John Alden.

48
00:02:05,100 --> 00:02:08,300
別以為有我對你父親的那點尊重
My respect for your father's memory

49
00:02:08,790 --> 00:02:10,680
你就可以在這里肆無忌憚
can only shield you so long.

50
00:02:12,450 --> 00:02:15,370
你今晚就要出征了  別在這惹事
It's a good thing you're mustering out tonight.

51
00:02:15,710 --> 00:02:17,900
不管你愿不愿意  西布里現在手握重權
Like it or not, Sibley's in charge.

52
00:02:17,900 --> 00:02:19,370
他或許能容忍你父親
He tolerated your father,

53
00:02:19,370 --> 00:02:22,610
但他可不會容你在這放肆
but he won't be happy till he sees you swing.

54
00:03:05,340 --> 00:03:07,070
你今天還沒學到教訓嗎
Didn't you learn anything today?

55
00:03:07,070 --> 00:03:09,400
是啊  是啊  如果多給我一個晚上的時間
Yes, yes, if I have to spend one more night

56
00:03:09,410 --> 00:03:11,580
接近喬治·西布里那個王八蛋
under the same stars as that bastard George Sibley,

57
00:03:11,580 --> 00:03:13,310
我會像殺豬樣宰了他
I will gut him like the pig that he is.

58
00:03:13,310 --> 00:03:16,520
你說這話會被當眾懲罰的
If -- talking like that will land you in the stocks.

59
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:17,680
沒機會了
No day soon.

60
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:20,260
我寧愿死在戰場上
I'd rather die fighting the French and the Indians

61
00:03:20,260 --> 00:03:22,580
也不愿在這被人侮辱
than get pissed on by the good souls of Salem.

62
00:03:23,230 --> 00:03:24,480
所以你是真要走了
So, you're really leaving.

63
00:03:27,210 --> 00:03:28,390
瑪麗  相信我
Mary, trust me.

64
00:03:30,220 --> 00:03:31,500
我會回來找你的
I will come back for you.

65
00:03:35,060 --> 00:03:35,720
看
Look.

66
00:03:38,620 --> 00:03:40,160
這是我僅有的了
This is all that I have.

67
00:03:41,130 --> 00:03:43,830
我以我父母之靈起誓
And I swear on my parents' grave.

68
00:03:46,300 --> 00:03:47,380
這就是我的誓言
This is my vow.

69
00:03:49,730 --> 00:03:52,130
這場戰爭頂多持續一年
This war will not last a year.

70
00:04:03,380 --> 00:04:04,150
前進
Forward!

71
00:04:05,750 --> 00:04:07,230
保持隊形  先生們
Stay in formation, gentlemen.

72
00:04:31,640 --> 00:04:33,260
大概就半天的路程
Isn't but a half-day's ride.

73
00:04:33,260 --> 00:04:34,380
我做不到
I can't make it.

74
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:36,210
我覺得我又要吐了
I think I'm gonna be sick again.

75
00:04:36,790 --> 00:04:39,110
沒事兒的  進去坐坐就好了
As soon as you sit down inside, it will settle.

76
00:04:39,110 --> 00:04:40,410
讓長者先行  小姑娘
Wait your betters, girl.

77
00:04:41,280 --> 00:04:42,740
愿上帝保佑你
Peace be upon you.

78
00:04:43,350 --> 00:04:44,350
你也是
And upon you.

79
00:04:48,070 --> 00:04:49,390
愿上帝保佑你
Peace be upon you.

80
00:04:49,620 --> 00:04:50,660
你也是
And upon you.

81
00:04:51,700 --> 00:04:54,210
雖然戰爭無情
Though there are things to be said for war.

82
00:04:54,210 --> 00:04:57,360
但對某些人來說  戰死沙場
Gives a certain kind of man someplace to end up

83
00:04:57,360 --> 00:04:59,160
遠比被處以極刑
other than the end of a brand...

84
00:04:59,960 --> 00:05:01,000
更有意義
or a rope.

85
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:03,900
終有一天你會感謝我的
You'll thank me one day.

86
00:05:08,430 --> 00:05:09,500
堅強點
Stay strong.

87
00:05:10,140 --> 00:05:11,910
今晚之后  一切都將結束
After tonight, it will all be over.

88
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:34,990
緹圖芭  等等
Tituba, wait.

89
00:05:35,940 --> 00:05:37,770
我改變主意了  我想回去
I've changed my mind. I want to go back.

90
00:05:38,330 --> 00:05:40,570
塞勒姆沒有那孩子的容身之地
There is no place for that child in Salem.

91
00:05:41,490 --> 00:05:45,000
喬治·西布里讓約翰·奧登戰死沙場
George Sibley drove John Alden off to die in the war.

92
00:05:45,630 --> 00:05:46,970
你覺得他要是發現了你懷著約翰的孩子
What do you think he's gonna do to you

93
00:05:46,970 --> 00:05:49,250
他會怎么對你
when he finds out you're pregnant with John's baby?

94
00:05:51,830 --> 00:05:53,750
不要害怕森林
Do not fear the woods.

95
00:05:54,790 --> 00:05:56,990
森林會照顧好那個小小的靈魂的
The woods are gonna take care of that little soul...

96
00:05:57,450 --> 00:05:58,290
還有你
and you.

97
00:06:10,050 --> 00:06:11,440
這是什么地方
What is this place?

98
00:06:11,440 --> 00:06:13,770
你若還想活  就好好躺著
You want to live? Lie still.

99
00:06:15,440 --> 00:06:16,410
求求你
Please.

100
00:06:16,980 --> 00:06:18,470
他留給我的只有這個孩子了
It's all that I have left of him.

101
00:06:18,470 --> 00:06:19,240
別出聲
Hush.

102
00:07:04,050 --> 00:07:06,160
不  等等  我不想這么做
No, wait. I-I-I don't want to do this.

103
00:07:06,690 --> 00:07:08,010
你別無選擇  瑪麗
You don't have a choice, Mary.

104
00:07:08,840 --> 00:07:09,590
求求你
Please.

105
00:07:09,590 --> 00:07:11,460
-這才是你想要的  -拜托
- This is what you want. - Please.

106
00:07:11,460 --> 00:07:12,790
這才是你想要的
This is what you want.

107
00:07:12,790 --> 00:07:15,000
-不  求你了  -讓他進去
- No...please. - Let him in.

108
00:07:27,120 --> 00:07:28,860
不要啊  拜托
No, please.

109
00:07:29,620 --> 00:07:30,420
別過來
Stay there!

110
00:07:52,430 --> 00:07:55,470
約翰  約翰  約翰  救救我
John. John. John, help me.

111
00:07:55,470 --> 00:07:56,650
救我
Help me!

112
00:07:58,730 --> 00:07:59,670
快告訴他
Now tell him.

113
00:08:00,500 --> 00:08:03,320
說吧  說這是你想要的
Say it. This is what you want.

114
00:08:03,320 --> 00:08:04,790
是  是
Yes. Yes!

115
00:08:04,790 --> 00:08:06,650
是我想要的
Yes!

116
00:08:41,030 --> 00:08:43,380
為了彌補你  整個世界都將是你的
All the world shall be yours in return.

117
00:08:44,540 --> 00:08:46,340
整個世界
All the world.

118
